    "Respondents voluntarily participated in the research and they were informed consent prior to their participation.",
    "The participants were informed that, due to the methodological nature of the network research, the data is collected by name, however, personal data will not be used when analyzing the data.",
    "After data collection, the names were hashed for data analysis.",
    "Network indicators and individual indicators anonymously provide sufficient information for research results and conclusions.",
